According to our ranks in the family,

149
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:37,280
you should address me as your aunt.

150
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,360
Both of us are descendants of

151
00:07:39,880 --> 00:07:41,600
the Emperor of Jing, Qi Hu.

152
