688
00:37:53,360 --> 00:37:54,000
Grandfather?

689
00:37:54,760 --> 00:37:55,200
No.

690
00:37:56,160 --> 00:37:57,080
Let her stay here.

691
00:37:58,440 --> 00:37:59,600
